OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773785475
OL,3,CFifa rejects Iran's request to move
OL,4,Cits World Cup matches from US to Mexico
OL,6,FFifa has turned down a request by
OL,7,FIran's men's football team for its
OL,8,FWorld Cup matches to be moved from the
OL,9,FUnited States to co-host Mexico this
OL,10,Fsummer.
OL,12,FIran's participation in the FIFA
OL,13,Ftournament in North America has been
OL,14,Fthrown into doubt after the US and
OL,15,FIsrael launched air strikes on Iran
OL,16,Flast month, which then retaliated with
OL,17,Fattacks on US bases in other Gulf
OL,18,Fcountries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
