FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773785475
OL,3,CFifa rejects Iran's request to move
OL,4,Cits World Cup matches from US to Mexico
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump said last
OL,7,Fweek he did not think it was
OL,8,F"appropriate" for Iran to participate
OL,9,F"for their own life and safety".
OL,11,FIn response, the president of Iran's
OL,12,Ffootball federation, Mehdi Taj, has
OL,13,Fsaid the team has requested that its
OL,14,Fmatches be played in Mexico.
OL,16,F"When Trump has explicitly stated that
OL,17,Fhe cannot ensure the security of the
OL,18,FIranian national team, we will
OL,19,Fcertainly not travel to America," Taj
OL,20,Fsaid in a statement posted on X.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773785475
OL,3,CFifa rejects Iran's request to move
OL,4,Cits World Cup matches from US to Mexico
OL,6,F"We are currently negotiating with
OL,7,FFIFA to hold Iran's matches in the
OL,8,FWorld Cup in Mexico."
OL,10,FA spokesperson from Fifa told ITV News
OL,11,Fit was in "regular contact" with all
OL,12,Fcompeting teams, "including IR Iran,
OL,13,Fto discuss planning for the FIFA World
OL,14,FCup 2026".
OL,16,FThe statement continued: "Fifa is
OL,17,Flooking forward to all participating
OL,18,Fteams competing as per the match
OL,19,Fschedule announced on December 6 2025."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
