PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773785475
OL,3,CFifa rejects Iran's request to move
OL,4,Cits World Cup matches from US to Mexico
OL,6,FA statement posted on the Iranian
OL,7,Fteam's Telegram also called for the
OL,8,FUS's removal from the tournament
OL,9,Finstead.
OL,11,FIt said: "The Iranian national team
OL,12,Falso qualified for this event with
OL,13,Fauthority and through consecutive
OL,14,Fvictories, becoming one of the first
OL,15,Fteams to reach this great tournament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
