FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773785475
OL,3,CFifa rejects Iran's request to move
OL,4,Cits World Cup matches from US to Mexico
OL,6,F"Certainly, no one can remove the
OL,7,FIranian national team from the World
OL,8,FCup. Rather, the country that should
OL,9,Fbe removed is the one that merely
OL,10,Fcarries the title of host but does not
OL,11,Fhave the ability to ensure security
OL,12,Ffor the teams participating in this
OL,13,Fevent."
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,20,FIran is currently due to play all
OL,21,Fthree group matches in the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
