PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773785475
OL,3,CFifa rejects Iran's request to move
OL,4,Cits World Cup matches from US to Mexico
OL,6,FMoving the games at this late stage
OL,7,Fwould be logistically difficult,
OL,8,Fparticularly considering the country
OL,9,Fcould still end up in the US in the
OL,10,Fknockout rounds, depending on where
OL,11,Fthey finish in their group.
OL,13,FThe men's team's request to move its
OL,14,Fmatches comes as two members of Iran's
OL,15,Fwomen's team, who were granted asylum
OL,16,Fin Australia earlier this month, have
OL,17,Fbeen pictured training with the
OL,18,FAustralian team, Brisbane Roar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
