PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773785475
OL,3,CFifa rejects Iran's request to move
OL,4,Cits World Cup matches from US to Mexico
OL,6,FFatemeh Pasandideh and Atefeh
OL,7,FRamezanisadeh were pictured smiling
OL,8,Fand wearing the club's colours as they
OL,9,Fposed alongside a women's elite squad
OL,10,Fin photos posted to Instagram on
OL,11,FMonday.
OL,13,FThe update came as the rest of Iran's
OL,14,Fsoccer delegation left Malaysia bound
OL,15,Ffor Oman, apparently capping a
OL,16,Ftumultuous episode that saw
OL,17,FAustralia's government offering most
OL,18,Fof the squad humanitarian visas after
OL,19,Fthe team was knocked out of the
OL,20,FWomen's Asian Cup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
