PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773785475
OL,3,CFifa rejects Iran's request to move
OL,4,Cits World Cup matches from US to Mexico
OL,6,FSeven women initially accepted the
OL,7,Fasylum offer before five changed their
OL,8,Fminds and said they would return to
OL,9,FIran.
OL,11,FBrisbane Roar, which plays in
OL,12,FAustralia's elite A-League Women's
OL,13,Fdomestic competition, posted a welcome
OL,14,Fto "Fatemeh and Atefeh" on Instagram,
OL,15,Falong with an emoji of a lioness, a
OL,16,Fnod to the name the Iranian players
OL,17,Fare known by.
OL,26,@vD@DOUvD@WO]
