OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773785475
OL,3,CFifa rejects Iran's request to move
OL,4,Cits World Cup matches from US to Mexico
OL,6,F"We remain committed to providing a
OL,7,Fsupportive environment for them whilst
OL,8,Fthey navigate the next stages,"
OL,9,FBrisbane Roar CEO Kaz Patafta wrote.
OL,11,FBoth women left comments on the post.
OL,12,F"Thank you for everything,"
OL,13,FRamezanisadeh wrote.
OL,15,FThe club declined further comment and
OL,16,Freferred all questions to Australia's
OL,17,FDepartment of Home Affairs.
OL,19,FThe Roar last week offered the women
OL,20,F"a place to train, play and belong" in
OL,21,Fa statement on social media.
